====Usage notes====
* Often used interchangeably in compounds with {{m|ja|器|tr=ki}} to indicate “machine”, with the distinction that {{lang|ja|機}} implies a larger machine, such as an airplane, while {{lang|ja|器}} implies a smaller device, possibly hand-held. Compare {{m|ja|飛行機|tr=hikōki||airplane}} with {{m|ja|検知器|tr=kenchiki||sensor, detector}}.

