* [[File:RYAKUJI_ki_01.png|class=skin-invert|40px]] A {{w|phono-semantic}} simplification from [[on'yomi]] of “ki” (katakana キ): 木 + キ (semantic plus simplified phonetic) – compare [[File:Ryakuji GI.png|class=skin-invert|30px]] for {{m|ja|議}} and [[File:RYAKUJI ma.png|class=skin-invert|30px]] for {{m|ja|魔}}/{{m|ja|摩}}. Note that [[キ]] is itself a Heian-period simplification of {{m|ja|幾}}.
